PrecisAppointment of PHILIP BAKER as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Mozambique; GLENN DAVIDSON as Ambassador of Canada to the Syriab Arab Republic; JONATHAN FRIED as Ambassador of Canada to Japan; ROBERT McDOUGALL as High Commissioner for Canada to the People's Republic of Bangladesh; and BARBARA RICHARDSON as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Zimbabwe, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Angola, and as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Botswana.
